snippet.title: Jaleco Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Original Evercade handheld. This cart contains 10 games from the Japanese developer, Jaleco. (Not to be confused with the Spanish arcade game developer, Gaelco)

Games in the cart:
00:00:08 - Astyanax (NES)
00:11:08 - Bases Loaded (NES)
00:19:55 - Brawl Brothers (SNES)
00:29:20 - City Connection (NES)
00:33:46 - Earth Defense Force (SNES)
00:38:15 - Operation Logic Bomb: The Ultimate Search & Destroy (SNES)
00:43:09 - Rival Turf (SNES)
00:49:24 - Super Goal! 2 (SNES)
00:56:32 - The Ignition Factor (SNES)
01:04:59 - Totally Rad (NES)

Jaleco, Astyanax, Bases Loaded, Brawl Brothers, City Connection, Earth Defense Force, Operation Logic Bomb, Rival Turf, Super Goal! 2, The Ignition Factor, Totally Rad (C) City Connection
